                    "body": "[~eerhardt] [~HashidaTKS] I have a small query for this change. I would be grateful if you can answer/ point me to the correct person to help me with this:\r\n\r\nAre we allowed to add a dependency to Arrow for an lz4 compression/ decompression library as part of this change? If not can you suggest another way forward?",
