                        "displayName": "Rishabh Rana",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Etc/UTC"
                    },
                    "body": "Thanks for your responses [~adreeve] and [~westonpace].\r\n\r\nPersonally, I am more inclined towards the approach that Eric and Weston have proposed. To avoid any unnecessary dependencies on Arrow. I will try to put the code together for the issue soon for a more fruitful discussion on the PR itself.\r\n\r\nThanks!",
